instructions: put the dinner plate on the center of table cloth
put the salad plate on the center of dinner plate
put the napkin on the center of salad plate
put the wine glass on the table cloth in the up right corner
put the water glass on the table cloth next to wine glass in right and position
put the salad fork on the table cloth in the left side of dinner plate, parallel to table cloth's side
put the dinner fork between salad fork and dinner plate and parallel to salad fork
put the dinner knife between wine glass and dinner plate, parallel to dinner fork
put soup spoon between dinner knife and wine glass and parallel to dinner knife
